g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但去到而家 有幾多個會話捐咗錢<br />\n當然 都可能驚捐完俾狗捉嘅<br />\n但講真賺完錢又無做過嘢 咁我做乜要食黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d185e7fcf86114dcf69215daaf05555e9b9bcf12","tid":2368180,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"46f4969a5e6aaf13d19b143265a2ac61eb078bf0","tid":2368180,"uid":130721,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:32:13.000Z","msg":"重點係食黃店完全唔明可以點樣有助 _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ 。<br />\n我睇到既只係一班生意人為左搵錢，話自己黃，但為左錢而做的事，又會令我好質疑佢地的初衷同埋有幾黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:26:42.000Z","msg":"所以搞好多嘩眾取寵:<br />\n<br />\n好似藍口罩唔畀入、<br />\n唔做藍媒訪問，並且要大聲講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但入貨就入湖北蛋<br />\n供應商理閪佢黃定藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己可以去淘寶<br />\n有料報可以搵東周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只做&quot;真&quot;香港人生意<br />\n有一套濕鳩審查機制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncheck身份證/口號/show黃店單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但乜原來香港人身份認同 <br />\n僅僅係身份證、口號、消費黃店？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請手足、賣手足乜乜物物產品<br />\n請手足嗰陣聲大大<br />\n唔做嗰陣要追糧<br />\n叫你去總公司/分公司<br />\n指定時間拎支票<br />\n搞一大輪 玩行政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足啲產品 <br />\nQC都未過 就推出嚟賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家長又唔介意<br />\n人手製作總有瑕疵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自由定價 $500入落錢箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n龍門有時真要多謝Marco<br />\n個手足資源中心摺柒咗<br />\n都唔完全係壞事"},{"pid":"509a314ee7dc